center_point <- function(n){
  fromto <- c(-1, 1)
  if (n < 4){
    fromto <- fromto/8
  } else if (n < 10){
    fromto <- fromto/4
  } else {
    fromto <- fromto/2
  }
  seq(from = fromto[1], to = fromto[2], length.out = n)
}
